#: ../../source/api/prepshot._model.storage.rst:2
msgid "storage"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.storage:1
msgid ""
"This module contains energy storage related functions. Symmetrical energy"
" storage system is considered in this module. It means that the energy "
"storage system has the same power capacity for charging and discharging."
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.storage:5
msgid ""
"Similar to the power discharging process, the charging power of storage "
"technology :math:`e` (:math:`{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{{c}}`) is also "
"limited by the existing installed capacity and technical minimum charging"
" power (:math:`{\\underline{{\\rm{POWER}}}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{{c}}`) as "
"follows:"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.storage:10
msgid ""
"{\\underline{{\\rm{POWER}}}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{{c}}\\times\n"
"{\\rm{cap}}_{y,z,e}^{\\rm{existingtech}}\\le{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{{c}}"
"\n"
"\\le {\\rm{cap}}_{y,z,e}^{\\rm{existingtech}}\\quad\\forall h,m,y,z,e\n"
"\\in {\\mathcal{STOR}}"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.storage:17
msgid ""
"The charging generation (:math:`{\\rm{charge}}_{h,m,y,z,e}`) and "
":math:`{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{c}` need to meet the following formula:"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.storage:20
msgid ""
"{\\rm{charge}}_{h,m,y,z,e}={\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{c}}\\times\n"
"\\Delta h{\\times\\eta}_{y,e}^{{\\rm{in}}}\n"
"\\quad\\forall h,m,y,z,e\\in {\\mathcal{STOR}}"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.storage:26
msgid ""
"Changes in stored electricity "
"(:math:`{\\rm{storage}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{energy}}`) in two successive "
"periods should be balanced by the charging "
"(:math:`{\\rm{charge}}_{h,m,y,z,e}`) and discharging "
"(:math:`{\\rm{gen}}_{h,m,y,z,e}`) processes:"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.storage:31
msgid ""
"{\\rm{storage}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{energy}}-\n"
"{\\rm{storage}}_{h-1,m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{energy}}\n"
"={\\rm{charge}}_{h,m,y,z,e}-{\\rm{gen}}_{h,m,y,z,e}"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.storage:37
msgid ""
"In addition, the initial (when :math:`h=h_{ m{start}}`) stored "
"electricity "
"(:math:`{\\rm{storage}}_{h=h_{\\rm{start}},m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{energy}}`) of "
"storage technology :math:`e` in each month of each year can be calculated"
" based on the proportion of the maximum storage capacity, as follows:"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.storage:43
msgid ""
"{\\rm{storage}}_{h=h_{\\rm{start}},m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{energy}}\n"
"={{\\rm{STORAGE}}}_{m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{energy}}\\times{{\\rm{EP}}}_e\\times\n"
"{\\rm{cap}}_{y,z,e}^{\\rm{existingtech}}\\quad\\forall m,y,z,e\\in\n"
"{\\mathcal{STOR}}"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.storage:50
msgid ""
"The instantaneous storage energy level "
"(:math:`{\\rm{storage}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{energy}}`) of storage "
"technology :math:`e` should not exceed the maximum energy storage "
"capacity, as follows:"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.storage:54
msgid ""
"{\\rm{storage}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{energy}}\\le{{\\rm{EP}}}_e\\times\n"
"{\\rm{cap}}_{y,z,e}^{\\rm{existingtech}}\n"
"\\quad\\forall h,m,y,z,e\\in {\\mathcal{STOR}}"
msgstr ""

